<lb n="0507a05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0507a06" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 115 [No. 99(924), No. 100(149)]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0507a07" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說馬有八態譬人經</title><note n="0507001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔出雜阿含別譯〕六字－【三】</note><note n="0507001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔出雜阿含別譯〕六字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507001"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">出雜阿含別譯</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0507a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0507a09" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">後漢<note n="0507002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西域三藏＝三藏法師【三】</note><note n="0507002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西域三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507002"><lem wit="【大】">西域三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app>支曜譯</byline>
<lb n="0507a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0507a1001">聞如是：</p><p id="pT02p0507a1004" place="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國行在祇樹給孤獨
<lb n="0507a11" ed="T"/>園，多比丘僧俱。佛告諸比丘：「馬有弊惡態
<lb n="0507a12" ed="T"/>八。何等八？一態者解&CB00650;韁時便掣車欲走；二
<lb n="0507a13" ed="T"/>態者駕車跳<note n="0507003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00568;＝踉【三】＊</note><note n="0507003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00568;＝踉【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0507003"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00568;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">踉</rdg></app>欲嚙人；三態者便舉前兩&CB00560;
<lb n="0507a14" ed="T"/>掣車走；四態者便&CB00569;車軨；五態者便人立持
<lb n="0507a15" ed="T"/>軛摩&CB01288;車&CB00230;行；六態者便傍行邪走；七態者
<lb n="0507a16" ed="T"/>便掣車馳走，得濁泥抵止住不復行；八態者
<lb n="0507a17" ed="T"/>懸<note n="0507004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02704;＝兜【宋】＊</note><app n="0507004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB02704;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">兜</rdg></app>餒之熟視不肯食，其主牽去欲駕之，遽
<lb n="0507a18" ed="T"/><note n="0507005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唅＝含【宋】</note><app n="0507005"><lem wit="【大】">唅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">含</rdg></app>&CB00078;噬欲食不能得食。」</p><p id="pT02p0507a1810" place="inline">佛言：「人亦有弊惡態
<lb n="0507a19" ed="T"/>八。何等為八？一態者聞說經便走不欲聽，如
<lb n="0507a20" ed="T"/>馬解&CB00650;韁掣車走時；二態者聞說經意不解，
<lb n="0507a21" ed="T"/>不知語所趣向，便瞋跳<app type="＊" source="0507003"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00568;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">踉</rdg></app>不欲聞，如馬駕車
<lb n="0507a22" ed="T"/>時跳<app type="＊" source="0507003"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00568;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">踉</rdg></app>欲嚙人時；三態者聞說經便逆不受，
<lb n="0507a23" ed="T"/>如馬舉前兩&CB00560;掣車走時；四態者聞說經便
<lb n="0507a24" ed="T"/>罵，如馬&CB00569;車軨時；五態者聞說經便起去，如
<lb n="0507a25" ed="T"/>馬人立持軛摩&CB01288;車&CB00230;行時；六態者聞說經
<lb n="0507a26" ed="T"/>不肯聽，&CB00376;頭邪視耳語，如馬傍行邪走時；七
<lb n="0507a27" ed="T"/>態者聞說經便欲窮難，問之不能相應答，便
<lb n="0507a28" ed="T"/>死抵妄語，如馬得濁泥便止不復行時；八態
<lb n="0507a29" ed="T"/>者聞說經不肯聽，反念<note n="0507006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬＝淫【三】</note><note n="0507006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬＝淫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507006"><lem wit="【大】">婬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">淫</rdg></app>泆多求不欲聽受，
<pb n="0507b" ed="T" id="T02.0115.0507b"/>
<lb n="0507b01" ed="T"/>死<note n="0507007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝八【明】</note><app n="0507007"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">八</rdg></app>惡道時，乃遽欲學問行道，亦不能復得
<lb n="0507b02" ed="T"/>行道，如馬懸<app type="＊" source="0507004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB02704;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">兜</rdg></app>餧之熟視不肯食，其主牽
<lb n="0507b03" ed="T"/>去欲駕之，乃遽唅&CB00078;噬亦不得食。」</p><p id="pT02p0507b0314" place="inline">佛言：「我說
<lb n="0507b04" ed="T"/>馬八態，惡人亦有八惡態如是。」</p><p id="pT02p0507b0413" place="inline">諸比丘聞經
<lb n="0507b05" ed="T"/>歡喜，作禮而去。</p>
<lb n="0507b06" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說馬有八態譬人經</jhead></juan></div1>
